<br>
Then one time we had someone bring in an alt that was much closer to level 50. All of a sudden we got a lot more agro than I was used to seeing in at level 60. Your level definitely affects agro radius, and there is no place where it makes a bigger difference than in fear.<br>
<br>
A group of level 60s can go in and never have more than 4 or 5 mobs in camp at the same time. A group of 50s doing identical things will have 20+ mobs in camp, just due to their larger agro radius.<br>
<br>
Plenty of people have talked strats above, so I wont go into that, but keep in mind that a lot of the people posting are level 60, so when they say something about agro, keep in mind they might be thinking about level 60 agro, and not the agro you will get with your group. The camp gets the agro of the lowest level person there, no matter the level of the rest of the people.<br>
<br>
-Iustus <p><BR>
